column1: Công Ty Cổ Phần Công Nghệ Flyer
column89: ['flyer is the first high-quality virtual interactive english testing platform for kids. we’re thrilled to build a global citizen qualification for vietnamese kids.we are looking for a specialist tester to join and build the next-generation web and native applications for our world-class flyer - english testing platform.- coordinate software testing processes, including creating and maintaining user acceptance testing documents.- write or modify existing testing plans, ions of testing results to facilitate it resolution of identified issues.- follow all established processes and procedures.- consistently meet or exceed expectations regarding the quality and quantity of work established by the company.- consistently meet attendance standards established by the company- interact appropriately with peers and other co-workers. contribute to building a positive team spirit.- perform other duties and projects as assigned.']

column1: CÔNG TY CỔ PHẦN SYNODUS
column89: ['contribute to agile meetings (stand-up, planning, reviews, etc.) to understand user stories and acceptance criteria.', 'write and execute test scenarios to ensure acceptance criteria are met.', 'evaluate test results and accurately record defects.', 'responsible for the system integration test in product deployment phase of the development lifecycle, ensure product go-live with high quality.', 'produce clear and concise testing documentation.', 'strong communication and personal skills, ability to interact and work well with members of other functional groups in a project team.', 'research new technologies and new methods in testing domain, apply and promote them.', 'corporate with po, ba to clarify requirements and document specifications for the team.', 'decompose business requirements to produce test conditions, mapping the scenarios to test cases.', 'responsible for the maintenance of test packs specifically relating to test cases.', 'responsible for developing, executing, and maintaining test design, test scenarios, test cases', 'document and evaluate test results and defects, track and manage defects and work with development team and business to troubleshoot issues.', 'provide feedbacks on all test activity progress to the team/manager/leader.', 'provide support with running regression testing and production smoke tests.']
